Package: sparx
Type: Package
Title: AI Pair-Programmer for RStudio
Version: 0.8.2
Authors@R:
    person("Mihir", "Curovana", email = "m@curovana.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An RStudio addin that adds an AI pair-programmer to RStudio.
    Describe what you want in English; sparx reads your script, session,
    and data, then generates R code, runs it, and iterates on errors.
    Supports both Anthropic (Claude) and OpenAI (GPT) models — switch
    providers from the chat panel, keys stored per-provider in the system
    keyring. Specialized for statistical workflows in medical research.
